        "meta_description": "I've wondered, since I started in Sweden, lowest league, once one reaches the top and becomes successful (winning national top division, UCL etc.) in a low reputation nation, how does one keep the players which will always want to move to bigger clubs? How do you hang on to your gems, to make a r...",
